      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KATIE LORRAINE (7) lines up for the first time. By Captaintreacherous and hails from the G J Quinlan, D J Quinlan stable. The driver has some work to do from this wide starting position. Has strong trial form coming into this. Will be ready to run a big race. EEBEEBEE (5) is racing very well with placings at her last five starts including a second at the latest appearance over 2190m at this track, beaten 4 metres after settling in the leading division and leading the field into the lane. Won't find this any harder and she can add to the solid recent record. MAC JAMES (4) must be considered after he finished third over 2190m at this track a week ago. IMAGUNNARESTNGO (2) is worth some thought based on her third over 2190m at this track two runs ago.",
